             were indicted, the first for <rs id="t17970426-78-off431" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17970426-78-off431" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17970426-78-off431" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17970426-78-cd432" type="crimeDate">6th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970426-78-off431 t17970426-78-cd432"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17970426-78-off433 t17970426-78-cd432"></join>, two metal ferrules, value 2s. 6d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17970426-78-victim629" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Taylor
                  <interp inst="t17970426-78-victim629" type="surname" value="Taylor"></interp>
